groovyx.net.http

Interface ToServer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApacheHttpBuilder.ApacheToServer, JavaHttpBuilder.Action.JavaToServer

    public interface ToServer

    Adapter interface used to translate request content from the HttpBuilder API to the specific format required by the underlying client implementation.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void toServer(InputStream inputStream)
      Translates the request content appropriately for the underlying client implementation.

    • Method Detail

      • toServer

        void toServer(InputStream inputStream)

        Translates the request content appropriately for the underlying client implementation. The contentType will be determined by the request.

        Parameters:
        inputStream - the request input stream to be translated.
